<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Login Token</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .token-box {
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 2px solid #007bff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .token {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #007bff;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        }
        .warning {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #856404;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Your Login Token</h1>
            <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
        </div>

        <p>You requested a login token for your account. Please use the token below to complete your login:</p>

        <div class="token-box">
            <div class="token">{{token}}</div>
        </div>

        <div class="warning">
            <strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> This token will expire in <strong>30 minutes</strong> from the time it was generated. Please use it promptly to access your account.
        </div>

        <p>If you didn't request this token, please ignore this email or contact our support team if you have concerns about your account security.</p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,<br>The PayBud Team</p>
            <p><small>This is an automated email. Please do not reply to this message.</small></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>